title: Tastes awful, super thick "drink" that won't pour out of bottle.
review: This is primarily sweetened with stevia and monkfruit, leaving a nasty aftertaste. This yogurt has substantial amounts of non-yogurt ingredients, like chicory root. The "yogurt" is so thick, it has to be squeezed from the bottle like toothpaste. If you want to get more than half the product out, you need to add water or milk to liquify it.
